<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1914-07-27T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1914-07-27T00:00:00-05:00" n="845" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d845">
                        <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 812.00/12637.</note>
                        <head>
                            <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Brazilian Minister</gloss> to
                                Mexico to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>.</hi>
                        </head>
                        <opener>
                            <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                        </opener>
                        <opener>
                            <dateline rendition="#right">
                                <placeName>
                                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Brazilian Legation</hi>, <lb/>
                                    <hi rend="italic">Mexico</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1914-07-27">
                                    <hi rend="italic">July 27, 1914</hi></date>.</dateline>
                        </opener>
                        <p>100. President Carbajal’s delegates have just left for Vera Cruz, whence
                            they will proceed at once to Tampico with instructions to negotiate at
                            any place agreeable to the Constitutionalist delegates in order to save
                            time. The change of itinerary was forcibly adopted because there is a
                            gap of nearly 200 kilometers this side of San Luis Potosí.</p>
                        <p>The President would like to know as soon as possible the names of the
                            Constitutionalist delegates.</p>
                        <closer>
                            <signed>
                                <hi rend="smallcaps">Cardoso de Oliveira</hi></signed>.</closer>
                    </div>
                    </body></text></TEI>